						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Press-Release-CTA-TOP-20-Innovations" title="Press Release - CTA TOP 20 Innovations " alt="document">Press Release - CTA TOP 20 Innovations </a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>







 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/cta-logo-small/574756-1-eng-GB/CTA-logo-small.png" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
	
	
	
  	






	 
  





	To capture the ideas and harness the potential of ACP innovators, the Technical Centre for Agriculture&nbsp;and Rural Cooperation ACP-EU (CTA) launched a call for proposals, in December 2013, to unearth and&nbsp;award 20 TOP innovations that are transforming smallholder farms in Africa, the Caribbean and The&nbsp;Pacific.&nbsp;<i>Journalists from ACP countries are welcome to engage in this one-of-its-kind contest by interviewing both innovators and end-users.</i>Download the press release (PDF) below.&nbsp;</p>
